title: Compilation skydive
creator_credit: Carl Boenish, Devon Chierighlio, Mike Vitlow and Philip Dauber
brief_description: Sky dive (U.S.); Carl Baenish, the world’s leading skydiving filmmaker shares some spectacular footage. “Spaceborne” (U.S.); An exciting selection of film footage taken during the manned moon flights. “The Wizard of speed and time” (U.S.); From out of his mountain cave blasts a Green Wizard moving at incredible speeds.
